<br>
LW1<br>
Aug Dex 2<br>
MoPain 2<br>
MoParry 1<br>
MoBlocking 1<br>
Aug Acuity 1<br>
Tireless 1<br>
and 3 banked points<br>
<br>
I mostly wanted the passives to make levelling easier and now I want to be more effective in RvR (and I'm tired of being mezzed all the time!) I'll have 16 points after respec. I'm thinking of taking:<br>
<br>
LW1<br>
Avoid Magic 2<br>
Purge<br>
Aug Acuity 1<br>
<br>
and then working on replacing Aug Dex/MoPain 2 possibly down the road and using my 2nd RA respec for IP when I have enough points. What would you do with your first 16 points (at 50 and to be most effective in RvR)?<br>
thanks,<br>
